'''Rekku n uɣesmar''' d'aṭṭan amaqran ig ttqissin iɣes umi neqqar [[Aɣesmar]] si tama n ufella d tin bwadda. Tifidiwin d rekku n yiɣes ittased seg seqsef (lexṣas) n idammen di tama uɣesmar. Lehlak agi at narnu ɣer tagayt n rekku n yeɣsan si lexṣas idammen. 

Llant aṭas n talɣiwin n rekku n yiɣes uɣesmar ig ttugelmen di 160 isegwasen iɛeddan.

==Amezruy==

Talɣa yettwasnen si zik, d tin id ismentes ttawil n ''phosphore [[Acebḥan|acebḥan]]'', tettwassen ɣur Legyiz s yisem n ''Phossy jaw'' tettwabgen-ed di timidi tis ''XIX'' d tazwara n tis ''XX'' ɣur ixeddamen n zalamiṭ s ufus. Assa s-umennuɣ anmali ad naf d akken aseqdec n ''phosphore [[Acebḥan|acebḥan]]'' yettwasenfel (yettwabeddel) s ''[[Azegwaɣ|uzegwaɣ]]'' iwakken ad sseḥbibren ɣef ixeddamen.

Ttawil n Radium daɣen yella d sebba n waṭṭan n Rekku [[Aɣesmar|uɣesmar]] yufatt-id i tekelt tamezwarut Dr H.S. Martland asegwas 1924 '''Radium jaw''' (Aɣusmar n radium), imi tixeddamin n tarmisin yesseqdacen taklut n radium cetkant ɣef uqraḥ n tuɣmas d [[Aɣesmar|uɣesmar]], ak-d lǧarḥ deg uksum n tuɣmas, kra isegwasen sin d tasawent at id eḍfer [[Tigẓelt ẓẓayen n yiɣes]] (Ostéosarcome).

Isegwasen agi ineggura, aṭṭan agi yarna ɣur imdanen isseqdacen s waṭas ttawil n ''bisphosphonates''.
